    "body": "### Steps to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ git clone https://github.com/haampie-throwaway/spack-status-code.git\r\n$ cd spack-status-code\r\n$ spack -e . install &> /dev/null && echo \"This should not be printed if the error code is correct\"\r\nThis should not be printed if the error code is correct\r\n$ spack -e . install --fail-fast &> /dev/null && echo \"This should not be printed if the error code is correct\"\r\n$\r\n```\r\n\r\n* **Spack:** 0.16.0-997-aa8e026242\r\n* **Python:** 3.8.7\r\n* **Platform:** linux-ubuntu20.04-zen2\r\n* **Concretizer:** clingo\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional information\r\n\r\n<!-- These boxes can be checked by replacing [ ] with [x] or by clicking them after submitting the issue. -->\r\n- [x] I have run `spack debug report` and reported the version of Spack/Python/Platform\r\n- [x] I have searched the issues of this repo and believe this is not a duplicate\r\n- [x] I have run the failing commands in debug mode and reported the output\r\n\r\nping @alalazo ",
